   Finding Out About Student Aid
   http://www.ed.gov/offices/OSFAP/Students/student.html
   Provides general information about the major federal student aid
   programs (who is eligible and how to apply), the new tax credits for
   education expenses, and other federal, state, and private sources of
   information.
   Related Topics: Preparing for college  Parents  Scholarships and
   grants  Student loans  State financial aid  Work-study  Budget your
   money  Taxes
   __________________________________________________________________


