   Funding Your Education
   http://www.ed.gov/prog_info/SFA/FYE/FYE01/
   If you have not yet started college or technical school, read this
   excellent publication. It will give you an introduction to Student
   Financial Aid Programs through the U.S. Department of Education and how
   to apply for them.
   Related Topics: Preparing for college  Parents  Scholarships and
   grants  Student loans  State financial aid  Work-study
   __________________________________________________________________


