   HOPE Scholarship & Lifetime Learning Credits (US Dept of Education)
   http://www.ed.gov/inits/hope/
   Background information on special federal education tax breaks for
   current students and life-long learners from the US Dept of Education.
   Related Topics: Parents  Scholarships and grants  Budget your money
   Taxes
