   The Hope Scholarship Credit and Lifetime Learning Credit (Notice 97-60)
   http://www.irs.ustreas.gov/prod/hot/not97-60.html
   Questions and Answers from IRS on the Hope Scholarship Credit and
   Lifetime Learning Credit, a deduction for student loan interest, and on
   creating Education Individual Retirement Accounts.
   Related Topics: Preparing for college  Parents  Scholarships and
   grants  Taxes
